des:
Lets get away from the cliches. Start your day with a list inspirational list of quotes that will make you think.
Get motivated that will inspire you. Jonathan Duhon believes that acknowledgement of our past greatness is key to future success. Just remember
When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote.

Inspire Me Please is part of The Me Collection by Jonathan Duhon
